"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Elon Musk, the Tesla [TSLA](https://www.forbes.com/companies/tesla) [-2.6%](https://www.forbes.com/companies/tesla) billionaire [who's helped the \\\"joke\\\" bitcoin rival dogecoin become a major cryptocurrency this year](https://www.forbes.com/sites/billybambrough/2021/11/23/sounds-shady-tesla-billionaire-elon-musk-challenges-binance-ceo-over-dogecoin-glitch/), has outlined exactly why he supports the memecoin over [the likes of bitcoin, ethereum and other cryptocurrencies](https://www.forbes.com/sites/billybambrough/2021/10/14/tesla-billionaire-elon-musk-signals-surprise-dogecoin-update-support-as-the-bitcoin-price-suddenly-surges/).\\n\\n*[Subscribe now to Forbes' CryptoAsset & Blockchain Advisor and discover hot new NFT and crypto blockbusters poised for 1,000% gains'](https://www.forbes.com/newsletters/forbescryptoassetadvisor/?utm_source=billybambrough&utm_medium=article&utm_campaign=cryptocodex)*\\n\\nThe bitcoin price has fallen sharply over the last month, [losing around 25% of its value and hitting the price of ethereum and most other major cryptocurrencies](https://www.forbes.com/sites/billybambrough/2021/12/03/300-billion-bitcoin-and-crypto-price-crash-after-stark-fed-warning-ethereum-bnb-solana-cardano-and-xrp-in-free-fall/)—including the meme-based dogecoin.\\n\\nMusk, speaking to *Time* magazine after it [named him](https://time.com/person-of-the-year-2021-elon-musk/) *Time's* 2021 Person of the Year, said he thinks dogecoin is better suited for transactions than bitcoin and has a \\\"much higher potential.\\\"\\n\\n**[Sign up now for the free](https://www.forbes.com/newsletter/cryptocodex/#2451f12d3534) *[CryptoCodex](https://www.forbes.com/newsletter/cryptocodex/#2451f12d3534)*—A daily newsletter for the crypto-curious. Helping you understand the world of bitcoin and crypto, every weekday**\",\"timestamp\":1639503351,\"title\":\"‘Much Higher Potential’—Elon Musk Reveals Why He’s Backing Dogecoin Over Bitcoin And Ethereum Amid Huge Crypto Price Crash\"},\"digest\":\"Ln5M1X9Ni8qYWul3eNWcgqQ2sUzDduw0OqhwMqAxHF8\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x4F222FCc7B45634559E9a40D1bDc1BafF6806786\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"c5xrj5Tlh_p8PeexKElGjT5KySiuyonlcqLccyC8A7o\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"rH5BgRIBVF6ZxR4z2uKrB2tnNMhojyRXpS5x02iHxQ0\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"QGltYfJ7exHuzbZBRB6vmJci5m5Sj9DyHEfjEdDBaryYyIkJNoSAhcC0iv6urXspMbjWDX_0978lOsMIKIvM2Q\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x85f8762a69ce2deae26ae801e6e1fa7db3c2c2057b9bfcafead7f9ae473fc379320aa0d8b7343f9b83914b8e9fd6114d0a9730f61ceb23cd2adedb4d2e4b70cc1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"c5xrj5Tlh_p8PeexKElGjT5KySiuyonlcqLccyC8A7o\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"rH5BgRIBVF6ZxR4z2uKrB2tnNMhojyRXpS5x02iHxQ0\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"Ln5M1X9Ni8qYWul3eNWcgqQ2sUzDduw0OqhwMqAxHF8\"}"